Alternatively, you can go to the \'Orders\' section, select the delivered order, and click \'Give Review\'. You can contact customer support through the Chat Support section in the app. How do I contact customer support? Additional Support If you wish to delete your account, go to Account, and select Delete Account. Follow the prompts to confirm the deletion. Please note - once the account is deleted, it cannot be restored. Go to the Profile section of the app and click on Edit Profile. You can update your name, email, phone number, and address information there. How do I request a refund? If you receive the wrong order or items are missing, go to the Orders section, select the relevant order, and click on Support. You can also contact customer support directly via chat support in the “Account” Section. What should I do if I receive the wrong order or items are missing? Issues and Refunds Can I change my delivery address after placing an order? If your order is significantly delayed, you can contact customer support through the app by clicking on Support or by chat support in “Account” Section. What if my order is late? After placing your order, you can track its status in real-time by clicking on the Track Order button in the Orders section. How do I track my order? How do I leave feedback or a review? How do I delete my Svaggy account? How do I update my profile information? Account Management To request a refund, go to the \'Orders\' section, select the order, and click on \'Support\'. A support agent will ask for your order ID and will be able to assist you with the request. Once an order is placed, changing the delivery address is not typically possible. However, you can contact customer support immediately to see if they can assist with your request. How do I use a promo code or discount? A: Select your promo code on the checkout page in the Promo Code section before placing your order. The discount will be applied to your total. A: Svaggy accepts major credit and debit cards and Svaggy Wallet. You can add or update your payment methods in the Payment section of the app. What payment methods are accepted? A: Yes, during the checkout process, you can select Schedule for Later and choose your preferred delivery date and time. Can I schedule an order for later? A: Select the restaurant you want to order from, choose your desired items, customize them if needed, and add them to your cart. Once you are ready, go to your cart, review your order, and click on Checkout. How do I place an order? Use the search bar at the top of the home screen to enter the name of the restaurant or type of cuisine you are looking for. You can also browse cuisine categories or use filters to narrow down your search. How do I search for restaurants or food items? Placing an Order Download the Svaggy app from the App Store or Google Play Store. Open the app and \'Sign Up\' with your phone number or email address. If you sign up with your phone number, you will receive an OTP via SMS. If you sign up with your email address, you will receive the OTP in your email. Enter the OTP to complete the sign-up process. Alternatively there is an option to sign up with your google and apple account. How do I create an account on Svaggy?
